The paper discusses regularization techniques for learning problems with matrices, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions multi-task learning, multi-class learning, and kernel learning, which are relevant to cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
